      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "VERGLAS (6) was below best last time but prior to that was narrowly beaten when fourth (22.96) in a Grade 5 at this track. Safe beginner but tricky box to overcome. Expecting sharp improvement this line-up. MY OCTAVIUS (2) was strong over this course and distance last time despite filling the minors, finishing 6 lengths behind Duran Queen in 23.14 and recording a new PB here. Should be in this for a long way. DEMENTIA (1) has been settling off the speed lately, finishing seventh (18.96) last time in a Grade 5 at Taree Super Track. Form from his last run is proving strong. Leading chance. HECTIC BLUE (8) must be respected despite an unplaced effort here most recently.",
